This is a folder for simulation in ModelSim.

Parameters can be changed in defines.vh.

For simulation you will have to do next steps:

  1) Prepare file with data and settings file 
     (use /py_utils/util_for_sim.py). 

  2) Make sure there are right names of files and parameters 
     in defines.vh.

  3) Run:
       
       vsim -do make.do

  4) In wave window you can see all signals in all modules. 
     In transcript window you can see result of searching.

  5) After all data passed thrue filter 
     DON'T FORGET TO STOP SIMULATION.

  6) Now you can see output file and check in witch lines of 
     input data file strings were found.
